The,service,provides,a,cloud,hosting,platform,for,training,and,education,providers,including,video,demos,and,related,media,resources,It,seeks,to,create,an,environment,for,managing,instructional,resources,and,learner,access,with,hosting,in,widely,distributed,data,centers,for,optimized,access,from,user,locations,API,methods,support,adding,and,updating,learner,user,accounts,with,assignment,to,appropriate,groups,for,access,permissions,Methods,synchronize,training,across,internally,hosted,systems,and,resources,managed,within,the,service,s,cloud,environment,The,API,also,handles,integration,with,systems,providing,learner,account,data,and,other,operating,information